channel.description:

item.title: TELE HELP! pl0x
item.dc:creator: @Skiddle Skiddle
item.description:
@Skiddle wrote:

Right click the tab on your server, it should say “case --”

Go to client.java I think that’s it, (I don’t use wL based servers) and search for that case it hould say the coords for the train place in there. just change them to the place you want.
